OL,3,CAnger as Oxford-Cambridge railway line
OL,4,Cclassified as England and Wales project
OL,6,FUsually, under the Barnett Formula -
OL,7,Fthe system used to fund the devolved
OL,8,Fnations - Wales, Scotland and Northern
OL,9,FIreland get extra money when more cash
OL,10,Fis spent on devolved issues like
OL,11,Feducation in England.
OL,13,FBut because the railways are not fully
OL,14,Fdevolved to Wales, the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment doesn't receive this money
OL,16,Fwhen it comes to rail infrastructure,
OL,17,Funlike Scotland and Northern Ireland.
OL,19,FThe issue hit the headlines when HS2
OL,20,Fwas also classified as an England and
OL,21,FWales project.
