OL,6,FThis has left some MPs feeling Wales
OL,7,Fis being shortchanged.
OL,9,FDavid Chadwick, Liberal Democrat MP
OL,10,Ffor Brecon, Radnor and Cwm Tawe, said
OL,11,Fon X: "There can be no justification
OL,12,Ffor this whatsoever. The UK government
OL,13,Fhas decided to deliberately
OL,14,Fshortchange Wales."
OL,16,FSpeaking to BBC Radio Wales, he said:
OL,17,F"I don't think anybody seriously
OL,18,Fbelieves that a railway from Oxford to
OL,19,FCambridge benefits rail users in
OL,20,FSwansea or Bangor.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
