OL,3,CAnger as Oxford-Cambridge railway line
OL,4,Cclassified as England and Wales project
OL,6,F"The Treasury is just using these
OL,7,Fclassifications to avoid paying Wales
OL,8,Fwhat it's owed, and that's the real
OL,9,Fpoint - somebody in the UK Government
OL,10,Fhas decided to shortchange Wales again
OL,11,Fby deliberately labelling this as an
OL,12,FEngland and Wales project to avoid
OL,13,Fgiving Wales any money, and that's why
OL,14,FI'm calling for this to be re-
OL,15,Fclassified as an England-only project."
