OL,6,FIn the Senedd, Plaid Cymru leader Rhun
OL,7,Fap Iorwerth challenged First Minister
OL,8,FEluned Morgan on the issue, saying it
OL,9,Fwas "confirmation that we have another
OL,10,FHS2 on our hands. You could not make
OL,11,Fthis up."
OL,13,FThe first minister responded: "Rail
OL,14,Finfrastructure is not devolved to
OL,15,FWales, you might want it to be, but
OL,16,Fthat is the situation it is in.
