OL,3,CAnger as Oxford-Cambridge railway line
OL,4,Cclassified as England and Wales project
OL,6,F"There is a pipeline of projects for
OL,7,FEngland and Wales. Are we getting our
OL,8,Ffair share? Absolutely not. Am I
OL,9,Fmaking the case? Absolutely. And I'm
OL,10,Fhoping we'll see some acknowledgment
OL,11,Fof that through the spending review.
OL,13,F"The Oxford- Cambridge line is part of
OL,14,Fthat broader rail infrastructure, HS2
OL,15,Fis an exception to that which is why
OL,16,Fwe're making the case in a separate
OL,17,Fway. "
