OL,6,FIn a written answer to David Chadwick
OL,7,FMP, the Department for Transport said:
OL,8,F"East West Rail is set to cover the
OL,9,Froute from Oxford to Cambridge and is
OL,10,Ftherefore part of the RNEP portfolio
OL,11,Fwhich covers funding for projects in
OL,12,FEngland and Wales. The RNEP portfolio
OL,13,Fcan be distributed to any scheme
OL,14,Facross England and Wales."
